title: American horror story asylum - Sister Jude meets The Angel of death
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: This season was the darkest, most conserversal season ever and I love it. I didn’t know whether to hate or love sister Jude until the very end. This season was the best season I swear
that signature laugh with husky-voiced lines, only Jessica can do it
Lange and Conroy, two geniuses. Not surprinsingly one of the best scenes I've ever watched in a TV show. It was a huge loss for the show to not having them as main cast anymore.

I still think it's so fucking cool Jude has an established relationship with Shacath. 

Such a nice touch seriously! Their chemistry is amazing and the entire dynamic of them sitting in a rinky dink cafe booth just discussing this like old buds was FUCKING AMAZING IDEA

“Aren’t you sick of me yet🥺💔?”
This scene was so fucking sad😭💔.
